premise_source_doc_sentence: From 1980 to 1983 , only Canadian actors were eligible for the award ; non-Canadian actors appearing in Canadian films were instead considered for the separate Genie Award for Best Performance by a Foreign Actor .
This uplifting family film also features beloved Canadian actors Megan Follows  (  `` Anne of Green Gables ''  )  , Roberta Maxwell and Lally Cadeau .
